Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:57.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}永遠を 永遠を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:57.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}永远 永远都会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:01:00.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}咲いても 枯れない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:01:00.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}绽放着永不枯萎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:05.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}この胸の ときめきは 尽きない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:05.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}胸口的跃动无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:08.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}誰よりも 誰よりも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:08.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}我比谁都 我比谁都
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:11.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}あなたを 見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:11.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}仔细的注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:17.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}果てしなくこの気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:17.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}这时的心情不会消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:21.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:21.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}直到永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这首歌是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.97,0:02:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,第三话 夕饷（晚餐）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我洗得很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,今天一整天发生很多事 累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,被子铺好了 今晚就先休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,薰的被子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有一套被子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我在旁边睡就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:02:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对薰太过意不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只要薰不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一起睡也没…没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,总…总之…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不要介意我 快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,薰的被子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 明天要回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能留在薰身边吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 离开家太九
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,家人也会担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而且…这件事太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是有婚约
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我…也只知道小时候的小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵对我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那么…那么请现在开始了解葵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,并且…也告诉我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我薰的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好了…快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,睡得真香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,唔？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是小葵的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,写的时候把2丁目5号写成5丁目2号了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,都破破烂烂的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵一定很珍惜地收藏着的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,为了来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,并且…也告诉我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我薰的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不能因为一时的冲动而越轨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,头脑得冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,即使说是婚约
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我连女朋友都还没交过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,突然有了妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 小葵也不是个坏女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 接受小葵的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我就得要回花菱家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:06:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,花菱 花菱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,薰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因为门开着…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,突然担心薰是不是走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不会走掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是 我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那么回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,被吟唱传承下来的优美词句
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不能再在这个家里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要保重 做个好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 等一下 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要丢下我 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,爷爷 妈妈要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,快留住妈妈 留住妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快 爷爷 妈妈要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你要哭哭啼啼到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,忘掉那种女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你是花菱家的继承者 懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不懂 我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那种事 我一点也不懂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 又是那个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么小葵会和我在一个被窝里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 不快分开的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好…舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然穿着和服看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵的胸部真丰满啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不想办法分开的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:09:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,万一被小葵误解了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好 出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不要逃 你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 相当漂亮的一击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,挑战者危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,等…等等…小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,千钧一发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,今次是腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 这个地方 放过我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,投降了 冠军投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,早…早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,薰…薰 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但为什么小葵在我的被子里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那是因为昨晚薰看起来很冷的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我靠在薰的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我睡着时有抱着什么东西的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,抱了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 用尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 薰也很冷的样子抱住我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我们算彼此扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是…不是什么彼此扯平的问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,请用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,看样子真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 擅自用了雪柜里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧 不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,应该没有什么材料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,能做出这样的菜 真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,等一阵我送你到车站
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我反正也要去大学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这…刚才跟家里联络过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,可以在这里多留些时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,会给你添麻烦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那倒不会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那么请让我送薰到车站
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,薰总是这个时间去大学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不 今天的课是第二节开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才可以这么悠哉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个…薰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,薰 什么时候会回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我想应该不会很晚 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想替薰做晚餐 可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,晚餐？我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事倒是应该我来拜托你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 晚饭以前我一定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,请慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好 要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,上次说这句话是什么时候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要些什么？太太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌 什么太太 我还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,请给我参鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这样都齐全了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 做晚饭前 先要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,薰真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,堆积了这样多衣服没洗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,（Aio三月号 获取他的心的方法）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵 会做怎样的晚饭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不是梦…吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 花菱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的聚餐不要迟到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,聚餐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,上次不是说过了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:14:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你当然会来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 今天突然有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么 花菱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说了摄影社的人全部出席的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,下次我一定会到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,跟薰在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,时间就会过得那么快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然稍微早了点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵 怎么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因为晚餐准备好了所以来这里等你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我应该没说过几点会回来才对…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,难道 你一直在这等？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,等了多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,一小时左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.53,0:16:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等了一小时！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在房间里等就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,想早一点和薰在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,想到再一下子就能在这里见到薰 时间一下就过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个请求…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,请求？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可以跟你牵手吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,薰的手真的好大…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,算大吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 但是我知道的薰的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是小时候的手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,当然会变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说的话 小葵也变了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我变了很多？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,变得很漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌 薰真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,请用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵 这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,筑前煮（注：地方菜名）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,合你口味吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃 非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.87,0:17:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,请多吃些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:17:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,能吃到这么好吃的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是离开花菱家后的第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 平常一直吃杯面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没有钱的时候就吃面包的硬边过日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,面包的硬边？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,难道只吃这些？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 男人的单身生活就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不吃营养的东西 薰会死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 请再多吃点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也有准备薰喜欢的烤鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢的烤鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么小葵知道我喜欢的菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细一看 全都是我喜欢的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵 为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢的菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那时的我一直注意着薰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我还知道很多其他薰的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,比如喜欢烤鱼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢的颜色是蓝色啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢短头发啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还有喜欢什么歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,难怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我还在奇怪为什么小葵知道妈妈唱的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我教她的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得啊 那首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,薰教的歌怎么能够忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也常常会唱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,只要一唱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就感觉到薰在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,无论怎样的痛苦都能熬过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,痛苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我为了能成为薰的妻子而努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因为像这样待在薰的身边是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,想为薰打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想为薰洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,想亲手为薰做饭吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只要是薰所希望的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都想要做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 一个人不停地说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,趁没冷掉赶快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.59,0:20:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,之前我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵对我的感情竟然到这个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还考虑得那么周到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,晚饭后洗澡水也准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真是体贴入微
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话 然后就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我来替你擦背
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要是连这种事都发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真的就会有点动心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是小葵 这也不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我来替你擦背 可以进来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,耶…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:33.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}この世で一番弱いものは何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:33.05,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}这世间最软弱的事物是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:42.29,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}それでも二人を守る為にある
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:42.29,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}即使如此 它还是为了守护我们而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:47.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}星の数程ある言葉から
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:47.49,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}即使是天上有着多少繁星的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.73,0:21:52.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}あなたの声で聞きたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.73,0:21:52.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我都想听听你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:56.89,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}だから愛だと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:56.89,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}所以这称之为爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:22:01.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}それは愛だと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:22:01.37,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那个也称之为爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:06.20,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}名も知れぬ花達と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:06.20,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}即使是跟不知名的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:11.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}同じ様な二人でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:11.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}一样的我们也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:15.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}恋をするって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:15.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}坠入了情网
